You ever pay any attention to how
developed countries are, do ya?

rows.label: tlk43200142_03_msg0002
rows.name:
If a country gets a bit more
developed, there's a whole lot
more jobs goin' for Merc Groups!

rows.label: tlk43200142_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Some o' those jobs might wind up
making the traders have more stuff
for sale too, I dare say!

rows.label: tlk43200142_03_msg0004
rows.name:
When you're doing a job, it's not just
a job! No! It's making the whole
country better! Ever think of that!

rows.label: tlk43200142_03_msg0006
rows.name:
I gotta do everything I can
to develop my country and make
the Merc Group stronger.
